    <div class="product-fullSpecialty-component">
    <div class="product_fullspecialty_component" data-component="product-fullspecialty-component">
        <productfullspecialtycomponent power="{&#34;title&#34;:&#34;HANDLING&#34;,&#34;desc&#34;:&#34;450NK crafted with the essence of a sports-grade street machine. Its design centers on agility, forming a dynamic ergonomic setting that leans towards a sporty disposition. The positioning of footrests and handlebars creates an optimal riding posture that balances both sporty and comfortable, ensuring the ideal experience for urban streets. With a sporty-oriented front Ø37mm upside down suspension swiftly absorbs impacts on uneven surfaces. Its robust support empowers effortless traversal through challenging terrains. Matched with CST high-performance tires that grip the ground with tenacity, negotiating tight corners and intersections becomes an effortless endeavor. Designed with a seat height of 795mm, the 450NK features a high-resilience seat cushion. Additionally, for those seeking a customized fit, alternative seat cushions of 785mm and 815mm are available as accessory options.&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;assets/images/PC_HANDLING.jpg&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;assets/images/WAP_HANDLING.jpg&#34;,&#34;isShow&#34;:&#34;true&#34;,&#34;productFeatures&#34;:[{&#34;value&#34;:&#34;Ergonomic Setting&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;isCountTo&#34;:false},{&#34;value&#34;:&#34;Ø37mm Upside Down Suspension&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;isCountTo&#34;:false},{&#34;value&#34;:&#34;CST High-Performance Tires&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;isCountTo&#34;:false},{&#34;value&#34;:&#34;795 Seat Height(785mm and 815mm Accessory)&#34;,&#34;image&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;&#34;,&#34;isCountTo&#34;:false}],&#34;powerData&#34;:{},&#34;powerDataReal&#34;:{}}" design="{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;undefined&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;undefined&#34;}" riding="{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;undefined&#34;,&#34;mbImage&#34;:&#34;undefined&#34;}" safety="{&#34;image&#34;:&#34;undefined&#34